#. @info:tooltip Tooltip for the gamut-correction action. The icon for this action is only visible in the UI while the color value within the corresponding spinbox is an out-of-gamut value. A click on the icon will change the spinbox’s values to the nearest in-gamut color (and make the icon disappear).
#: colordialog.cpp:483
msgctxt "PerceptualColor::ColorDialogPrivate|"
msgid "Click to snap to nearest in-&gamut color"
msgstr "לחיצה כדי להיצמד לצבע כחלק מה&גאמוט"

